I am broke - Have no money

1. For a good reason, I am broke.
2. Seriously, I am flat broke.
%
Brush up on - practise it or improve your knowledge of it.

1. Yes, but I have to brush up on my driving.
2. Eleanor spent much of the summer brushing up on her driving.
